{
  "stem": "7069.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They have their-- they have-- they should be just as proud of theirs as we are of ours.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So she always preached the respect for other religions and other people to us, when we were small.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she saw to it that when the time came-- like, about two years before-- before my Bar Mitzvah she saw to it that, of course, I would have my Bar Mitzvah lessons.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course that forced me-- yes, it forced me, naturally, easily accepted-- [? so ?] to go regularly to the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It [? was a necessity ?].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Our Rabbi Alexander, you weren't-- you wouldn't dare to miss a Friday night or shabbos morning service-- shabbat morning service.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Do you remember your Bar Mitzvah?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes, I remember my Bar Mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my Bar Mitzvah was in a very, very simple manner.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, at those days, particularly in Germany-- I don't know exactly how it was here in America.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But at those days, Bar Mitzvahs were never celebrated on a big level as it is nowadays.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's only usually-- usually the immediate family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And our family was very small at that time, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we celebrated in-- in on our home, after we were done with the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Certainly celebrated in our home afterwards, on-- on a small level, with only the immediate, very, very small family there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, by the time of my Bar Mitzvah, Hitler was in power already for one year.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Things, by that time, became quite tight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By that time, our mother had lost her job because she was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because Hitler had soon declared that non-Jewish employers would not be allowed to have Jews working for them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so she lost her job.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
